channel.title: Firefighters film UFO in China
channel.description:
It's scary how much it sounds like what I saw, except what I saw was a little more bright and definitely faster. Not just a sighting I've had, one that almost the entire town of Waltham Quebec saw one night (where I was at the time..)
I still think there's a logical explanation to everything. But it doesn't change the fact that it was still an unidentified flying object.
http://www.allnewsweb.com/page1901902.php.php
I would like to see the video when it comes out.
